Text:
@notwarnus and anyone else getting this error: ""The ordinal 5360 could not be located in the dynamic link library xlive.dll" anyone know what to do?"

The DLL file can be found below.  Download it under the advanced users tab (as the zip file) and extract it to your Fallout 3 installation directory.  Retry installing the 1.7 patch and you should be good to go, that's what I did!

http://www.dll-files.com/dllindex/dll-files.shtml?xlive
